The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Asia Cup from June 24
                                                   Asia Cup from June 24
            OUR SPECIAL CORRESPONDENT                      
	Sydney: Karachi and Lahore will host the next edition of the Asia Cup, from June 24-July 6.         
	The tournament is on... Theres no confusion... The day-night matches, however, will only be played in Karachi and Lahore, the Asian Cricket Councils chief executive, Syed Ashraful Huq, told The Telegraph.         
	The last edition was hosted by Sri Lanka at the start of the 2004-05 season.                                                                                                                       
